sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Surface as Assistant or Widget Surface
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Session as Session and Continuity Layer
    participant Workflow as Workflow Runner
    participant Agent as Agent Runtime
    participant Provider as Model or Tool
    participant State as JSON State

    User->>Surface: Submit message
    Surface->>API: POST /sessions/{session_id}/messages
    API->>Session: append_session_message(...)
    Session->>Session: Load recent tail and active continuity summary
    Session->>Session: Build grounding and bounded carry-forward context
    Session->>Workflow: start_workflow(...)
    Workflow->>Agent: run_agent(...)
    Agent->>Provider: Call model or allowed tool
    Provider-->>Agent: Result
    Agent->>State: Persist workflow, trace, memory, and artifact state
    Session->>State: Persist session, continuity summary refs, and compaction metadata
    API-->>Surface: output, workflow status, ids
    Surface-->>User: Render reply or waiting state
